It worsens as he meets resistance while trying to discuss his findings with friends, family, and his wife, pushing them all to the breaking point. As a last ditch effort to save his marriage, he makes a movie to show his wife. It worked. Her eyes opened. It also worked with his sister. And mom. And friends. And most everyone who's seen it. Now you can see the film that restored his life, restored his sanity, and finally got his loved ones to open their eyes to how they've been deceived by the official narrative of 9/11.
